{"name":"Lesser Magic (Skywalk)","permission":{"default":0,"fvu77M1xxrZr85ZK":3},"type":"talent","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>You know a spell common to all types of magic. Lesser Magic is unusual in that it is not one talent, but many, and each must be acquired individually. Each Lesser Magic talent is a separate spell, with the spell name noted in parenthesis. For example, Lesser Magic (Dispel) is a different talent than Lesser Magic (Skywalk). You must have a Petty Magic talent before you can learn a Lesser Magic talent.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"bonus":{"value":null,"display":"You know a spell common to all types of magic. Lesser Magic is unusual in that it is not one talent, but many, and each must be acquired individually.","target":"","constant":false},"relatedSkills":[""]},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"nyWtqQPBT5C2xO9w"}
