{"name":"Dark Magic","permission":{"default":0,"fvu77M1xxrZr85ZK":3},"type":"talent","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>You know how to manipulate Dhar (black magic) to fuel yourspells. Using Dark Magic gives you more power, but is much more dangerous. When you cast a spell, you can opt to use the energy of Dhar to fuel it. When making a Casting Roll for a Dark Magic spell, you roll an extra d10 and drop the die with the lowest result. However, all dice count for the purposes of Tzeentch’s Curse. For example, a wizard with Magic 2 who casts a dark magic spell rolls 3d10 and uses the highest two dice for his Casting Roll. All three dice are used to determine Tzeentch’s Curse. If he rolled a 6, 6, and 6, the Casting Roll would be 12 (6+6), but the spell would trigger a Major Chaos Manifestation. You must use Dark Magic when casting a Dark Lore spell.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"bonus":{"value":null,"display":"When you cast a spell, you can opt to use the energy of Dhar to fuel it","target":"","constant":false},"relatedSkills":[""]},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"savbA5Go6fHLv9bA"}
{"name":"Frenzy","permission":{"default":0,"fvu77M1xxrZr85ZK":3},"type":"talent","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>You can incite yourself into a frothing rage. You must spend 1 round psyching yourself up (howling, biting your shield, etc.). The next round you lose control and go berserk, gaining a +10% bonus to Strength and Will Power but a –10% penalty to Weapon Skill and Intelligence. You must attack the nearest enemy in melee combat, all attacks must be all out attacks, charge attacks, or swift attacks, and you may not flee or retreat. You remain in this frenzied state until the combat is over.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"bonus":{"value":null,"display":"You must attack the nearest enemy in melee combat, all attacks must be all out attacks, charge attacks, or swift attacks, and you may not flee or retreat. You remain in this frenzied state until the combat is over.","target":"","constant":false},"relatedSkills":[""]},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"t3R7zgeVkApxSMxY"}
{"name":"Contortionist","permission":{"default":0,"fvu77M1xxrZr85ZK":3},"type":"talent","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>You can bend and manipulate your body in a myriad of unnatural ways. You gain a +10% bonus on relevant Performer Skill Tests and a +20% bonus on Agility Tests to escape from bonds, squeeze through narrow openings, and so on.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"bonus":{"value":null,"display":"You gain a +10% bonus on relevant Performer Skill Tests and a +20% bonus on Agility Tests to escape from bonds, squeeze through narrow openings, and so on","target":"","constant":false},"relatedSkills":["Performer (Acrobat)","Performer (Actor)","Performer (Clown)","Performer (Comedian)","Performer (Dancer)","Performer (Fire Eater)","Performer (Jester)","Performer (Juggler)","Performer (Mime)","Performer (Musician)","Performer (Palm Reader)","Performer (Singer)","Performer (Storyteller)"]},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"wS3IvOEfWtYXEK6U"}
{"name":"Disarm","permission":{"default":0,"fvu77M1xxrZr85ZK":3},"type":"talent","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>If you hit with a melee attack, you may attempt to disarm your opponent instead of inflicting damage. Make an Opposed Agility Test. If you win, your opponent is disarmed and the weapon drops to the ground. It can be picked up with the ready action. If your opponent wins, he retains his weapon. Natural weapons (teeth, claws, etc.) cannot be disarmed.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"bonus":{"value":null,"display":"If you hit with a melee attack, you may attempt to disarm your opponent instead of inflicting damage.","target":"","constant":false},"relatedSkills":[""]},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"y83p8aJlBbvN7wVL"}
