{"name":"Strike to Stun","permission":{"default":0,"fvu77M1xxrZr85ZK":3},"type":"talent","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>First, you must make a Strength Test. If that is successful, your opponent must make a Toughness Test, with a +10% bonus for each AP on his head. If he fails, your opponent is stunned for 1d10 rounds. Stunned characters cannot take any actions and cannot dodge.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"bonus":{"value":null,"display":"If you hit with a melee attack, you may attempt to stun your opponent instead of inflicting damage.","target":"","constant":false},"relatedSkills":[""]},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"9umRAETxbwJkAEPh"}
