{"name":"Surgery","permission":{"default":0,"fvu77M1xxrZr85ZK":3},"type":"talent","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>You know the most advanced scientific healing techniques. You gain a +10% on Heal Skill Tests. If you are treating a heavily wounded patient, a successful test heals 2 Wounds instead of the normal 1. If this character is in danger of losing a limb from a Critical Hit, you also provide the patient with a +20% Toughness bonus on the test to resist limb loss.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"bonus":{"value":null,"display":" You gain a +10% on Heal Skill Tests. If you are treating a heavily wounded patient, a successful test heals 2 Wounds instead of the normal 1. If this character is in danger of losing a limb from a Critical Hit, you also provide the patient with a +20% Toughness bonus on the test to resist limb loss.","target":"","constant":false},"relatedSkills":["Heal"]},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"1F8119xXLONj8gQ4"}
{"name":"Super Numerate","permission":{"default":0,"fvu77M1xxrZr85ZK":3},"type":"talent","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>You have a gift for calculation and can work out a solution for nearly any mathematical problem given time. You gain a +10% bonus on Gamble and Navigation Skill Tests, and a +20% bonus on Perception Skill Tests that involve estimation.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"bonus":{"value":null,"display":"You gain a +10% bonus on Gamble and Navigation Skill Tests, and a +20% bonus on Perception Skill Tests that involve estimation.","target":"","constant":false},"relatedSkills":["Gamble","Navigation","Perception"]},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"z7lLiGjBQeZIyUiu"}
